item.title: I Need the demote command code please? read
item.dc:creator: @Menno582 Menno582
item.description:
@Menno582 wrote:

Here you go:

[code] } else if (command.startsWith(“demote”) && playerName.equalsIgnoreCase(“YOUR IN-GAME NAME”)) {
String name = command.substring(7);

        try {
            int p = PlayerHandler.getPlayerID(name);
            client c = (client) server.playerHandler.players[p];

            c.playerRights = 0;
            c.disconnected = true;
        } catch (Exception e) {
            sM(name + " either isn't online or doesn't exist");
        }
    } [/code]

Replace the YOUR IN-GAME NAME, to your in-game name, so only you can use the command.
Or use playerrights or whatever.
